name: Animal Hooded Towels
description:
These fun applique towels are perfect companions to bath, beach, or pool time!! It features a full size towel and hood, plus wash cloth!!

This towel makes a great gift and includes name personalization. I have many towel designs and colors available, please convo me to ensure I can acccomdate your request! The animals are also totally customizable with your choice of colors!

Please leave name and color choices in note to seller during check out!

name: Custom Party Hat
description:
Happy Birthday!!! Let the special birthday boy or girl party in style!! From 1 to 101!

This custom birthday party hat stands at 7.5 inches tall and is personalized with appliqued birthday number and embroidered name. Hats are finished with elastic band standard, but coordinating ribbon strands for tying are also available. YOU CHOOSE the color/theme combinations. Looking for other finishing touches, korker ribbon, ric rac, pom poms, all available upon request!!

Dont forget to order a made to match onesie for the big day!!! These hats are the perfect keepsake and look great in shadow boxes!

Please leave color/theme, name and number for hat in notes to seller when checking out!

name: Personalized Ribbon Onesie
description:
This dressed up onesies is embellished with a large 1.5" ribbon and accenting bow. All ribbon is sewn down to provide a clean line and durability. Above the ribbon accents a name or monogram is embroidered to finish of this personalized outfit! 

You choose the ribbon color/theme! A special no itch lining protect skin from the embroidery.

Available in sizes 0-3 to childrens 7/8.

Make an adorable baby shower gift or birthday present! Round out the gift with a matching set of boutique bloomers! http://bubblegummonkeys.bigcartel.com/product/boutique-monogram-bloomers-with-bows

Please leave shirt size, color requests, and name in notes to seller during check out!

name: Boutique Monogram Bloomers with Bows
description:
These boutique bloomers are perfect for under a dress or to be worn with a t shirt! The bloomers feature soft elastic waist and double seat, and eyelet edging.

Bloomers are done in your choice of Inital with name or traditional 3 letter monogram. Thread colors of your choice with coordinating bow accents at the corners.

The bloomers are perfect for baby shower gifts, newborn pictures, birthday presents, and so much more.

Please leave name and color choices in notes during checkout.
